## Branching

**Branching enables parallel development for developers**

Benefits:
- Multiple developers work on different features simultaneously
- Isolation of work without affecting main codebase
- Safe experimentation with new ideas
- Clean separation of concerns

![Git Commands and Branching Diagram 3](pg3.jpg)

